CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 8, 1969, pg. 16 reads: "Married 25 Years - Mr. and MRs. James (Betty) Fowler, smile happily for the photographer. They celebrated 25 years of happy wedded bliss on Jan. 20.   Both are former employees of the Courier. - Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of James and Betty Fowler posed in domestic interior for Twenty-fifth wedding anniversary
